title: Guests
description: The default group that all visitors are assigned to unless they're logged in.

title: Registered
description: After registration, all users are placed in this group by default.

title: Super Moderators
description: These users can moderate any forum.

title: Administrators
description: The group all administrators belong to.

title: Awaiting Activation
description: Users that have not activated their account by email or manually been activated yet.

title: Banned
description: The default user group to which members that are banned are moved to.
